description: Restrictions were imposed on people in County Kildare on 8 August after a spike in coronavirus cases.
title: Coronavirus restrictions lifted in County Kildare
title_page: Coronavirus restrictions lifted in County Kildare - BBC News
maintext: The Irish government said that there were 75 cases recorded in the county in the week to 29 August compared to 238 cases notified in the week to 8 August, 170 cases in the week to 15 August, and 159 cases in the week to 22 August.
